  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this project is to provide life-saving food security assistance to vulnerable communities in 12 governates. This WFP project provides voucher assistance to 2.285 million people, including 607,000 women, 626,000 men, and over 1,000,000 children. This project is part of an $80 million CERF allocation to support cash programming in response to increasing food insecurity in 6 countries.</narrative>
